data.description: This 5 BR, 4 BA home PLUS BONUS ROOM sits on over an acre lot in Callahan in the Reserve a Deer Run - plenty of room for a growing or extended family. OPEN RURAL, LOW HOA, NO CDD, COUNTY TAXES! Fresh landscaping and double front doors welcome you to the customized Fleming II floor plan featuring five bedrooms and three full baths on first floor, plus generous bonus room with full bath and walk in closet on second. Hand scraped wood flooring throughout main living area complements the Chef's kitchen with working island, granite counters, pantry, new cooktop, double ovens, farm sink, and floating shelves w/ subway backsplash. The lot offers room for a barn, garage, or workshop for all the toys/RV/Boat. Chicken coop & pergola convey. Free flowing 600 ft deep Artesian well, 2 hot water heaters, dual zone AC, water softener + electric fence. Callahan Public Schools and quick access to I-95 / Jacksonville and an easy commute to Yulee & Historic Fernandina Beach. Partial VA assumable loan.
